  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "I scanned over the accepted paper lists of top machine learning and data mining conferences for interests in graph learning. We also add a snippset tutorial [Parse Website](./ParseWebsite.md) to teach you **how to obtain the titles and authors from the official conference website**.",
    "context": "I scanned over the accepted paper lists of top machine learning and data mining conferences for interests in graph learning. We also add a snippset tutorial [Parse Website](./ParseWebsite.md) to teach you **how to obtain the titles and authors from the official conference website**.\n\n- ## Recommended paper list\n  - [Dynamic (Temporal) Graph Learning Reading List](https://github.com/doujiang-zheng/Dynamic-Temporal-Graph-Learning-Reading-List)\n  - [Awesome-Human-Mobility-Science-Paper-List](https://github.com/Star607/Awesome-Human-Mobility-Science-Paper-List)\n\nWe also create the reading lists for [2022](./Graph-Learning-2022.md), [2023](./Graph-Learning-2023.md), and [2024](./Graph-Learning-2024.md) for convenience.",
